{"tid":1385912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（請廣傳 和 學習）今日不合作活動 成功例子","createTime":"2019-07-30T07:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T14:55:05.000Z","uid":278414,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4d6b2bd0be79446edc88b52f50d4825f571ce875","tid":1385912,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:57:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10217445951073941&amp;id=1030234114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10217445951073941%26id%3D1030234114&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmIwx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=8d9ed4d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10217445951073941&amp;id=1030234114</a><br />\n<br />\n今次好成功<br />\n大家可以參考一下 細心學習<br />\n<br />\n不合作活動 是要繼續進行<br />\n但需要包裝<br />\n就可以贏得乾脆利落<br />\n問題在於肯唔肯有耐心、耐性進行<br />\n有時候<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔洗下下燥底爆seed 狂鬧反對聲音</span><br />\n<br />\n最後一個<strong>有禮貌既致歉</strong>、<strong>有禮儀既鞠躬</strong> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">贏得全場支持掌聲</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a660ea44167cab45deedfdf637c8e80e9d49ac","tid":1385912,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:58:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c727f916bec737d23bf06706a1acf1a7e96e303","tid":1385912,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:59:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ed241d79c27cfd8b32461afd7d901dbccedab62","tid":1385912,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:00:24.000Z","msg":"個藍衫啊伯聽到呆呆地 最後要拍手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5566723d0e8e4d03c2221047840525c8a38fe7c","tid":1385912,"uid":278414,"like":